ul.li:
Insert the required attributes -  inserts
        automatically the required attributes taken from the DTD or XML Schema. This option is applied also in the
            Author mode of the XML editor;

Learn attributes values -  learns the
        attribute values used in a document. This option is applied also in the Author mode of the XML
          editor;

Learn on open document -  automatically
        learns the document structure when the document is opened. This option is applied also in the
            Author mode of the XML editor;
